ABOUT

  'fserv' is a minimal lua http runtime, with a focus on

    - server side rendering
    - static files
    - archivability

DEMO

  see my website's source [0]

  [0] https://github.com/slmjkdbtl/space55.xyz

BUILD

  $ make

    builds locally under 'build/'

  $ make install

    installs the binary to /usr/local/bin

USAGE

  $ fserv ?.lua

    will run the lua file

  $ fserv

    without args will serve static files in current directory, use PORT env variable to set port, defaults to 80

